    "title": "Mid-Level Fleet Manager at Gati",
    "description": "Join the Gati family as a Fleet Manager in Allahabad. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Gati:\nGati is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Learning & development budget\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Allahabad, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Gati!",
